715212f-a.title: Manhattan: 120th Street (East) - 1st Avenue
715212f-a.text:
East 120th Sereet, at, adjoining and east of the N.E. corner of First
Ave. The gas station shown, occupies building plots Nos. 2342-2344 First
Ave. Prominent building shown at Nos. 415-431 East 120th Street, is P.S.
No. 80.
August 18, 1936.
P. S. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
